entries.femaleVariant: Someone ratted and we won't know who. Period.
Fuck that. We'll find out. And do you know why?
Don't believe the pigs could do this without help, resources.
But this smells like Militech to me. Something isn't right.
Dude, no one will know. Just cover it, move stuff around.
No no, Dina would kill me if she knew.
Hey... you know those Polish guys at the docks? That Sobotka?
He'll tag a container, we grab some fruit – with goodies inside – split the earnings. Easy. No sweat.
Shit, I don't know... Always sounds easy.
Think about where that money could take you and Dina.
I'm thinking about what hole it could bury us in.
Because pigs always squeal. The police can't keep their source secret forever.
I need to send the summary to our gonk downstairs.
